com.hotels.styx.api

Interface StyxObservable<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of object published

    public interface StyxObservable<T>
    Exposes a transformation API for HTTP interceptors.

    This interface provides a is *not* intended for plugins to extend.

      • asCompletableFuture

        CompletableFuture<T> asCompletableFuture()
        Converts this observable to a completable future. Note that in order to do this, it must publish exactly one element before completing, otherwise the future will complete exceptionally, with the error being:
        • NoSuchElementException if it completes without publishing any elements.
        • IllegalArgumentException if more than one element is published.
        Returns:
        a completable future
